{"tid":2517962,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼剃頭 斑禿  跪求治療方法","createTime":"2021-05-05T16:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T16:32:47.000Z","uid":103603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f6ae782ce2d35fabde56e2586515a5bef368b9c","tid":2517962,"uid":103603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:30:01.000Z","msg":"有冇人試過有咩方法可以快啲好快？<br />\n我以前都試過一次 之後去屋企附近有間護髮睇左大概半年就好 幾千蚊一個plan 但而家搵唔返個間野<br />\n坊間既護髮好多都sell package 又局你一次過買成幾皮野 <br />\n<br />\n我而家有睇皮膚科 佢係建議我打類固醇針 我又唔太想<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知有咩好方法或者一啲冇咁呃錢既護髮中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a32426f4bae86b35dd625caef729c6226a7623e","tid":2517962,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"搽類固醇藥膏,滴藥水,信醫生好過"}]}